<h2 id="三、问题-2-java-8-instant-类型序列化报错" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#三、问题-2-java-8-instant-类型序列化报错"><span>三、问题 2：Java 8 Instant 类型序列化报错</span></a></h2>
<h3 id="_1-现象描述-1" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-现象描述-1"><span>1. 现象描述</span></a></h3>
<p>SBA 后端日志抛出序列化异常：</p>
<div class="language- line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code" v-pre=""><code class="language-"><span class="line"><span>com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.exc.InvalidDefinitionException: </span></span>
<span class="line"><span>Java 8 date/time type `java.time.Instant` not supported by default: </span></span>
<span class="line"><span>add Module "com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype:jackson-datatype-jsr310" to enable handling </span></span>
<span class="line"><span>(through reference chain: ...->Application["statusTimestamp"])</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>原因是 SBA 的 <code v-pre>Application</code> 类中 <code v-pre>statusTimestamp</code> 字段为 <code v-pre>Instant</code> 类型，而 Jackson 默认不支持 Java 8 日期类型。</p>
<h3 id="_2-根因分析-1" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-根因分析-1"><span>2. 根因分析</span></a></h3>
<p>Jackson 对 Java 8 日期时间 API（<code v-pre>java.time</code> 包）的支持需要额外模块 <code v-pre>jackson-datatype-jsr310</code>，且需手动配置序列化规则。即使引入模块，若未自定义 <code v-pre>Instant</code> 格式，还可能出现时区偏移或格式不符合需求的问题。</p>
<h3 id="_3-解决方案-完整配置-java-8-日期支持" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-解决方案-完整配置-java-8-日期支持"><span>3. 解决方案：完整配置 Java 8 日期支持</span></a></h3>
<h4 id="步骤-1-确保依赖引入" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#步骤-1-确保依赖引入"><span>步骤 1：确保依赖引入</span></a></h4>
